- #124 Embedding screenshots in JSON and HTML reports
- #129 success and failed properties in after and around hooks
- #179 Hooks as steps
- #159 Callback.fail() not supported in hooks.

It also fixes: 
- #110 Errors within Before and After hooks should make the scenario fail
- #181 visitRow function is unused

